<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Agenda - Registration Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;700&display=swap');

    body {
      font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #8e44ad;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header img {
      width: 120px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #8e44ad;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .features {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .feature {
      text-align: center;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .feature img {
      width: 50px;
      height: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .social-links {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .social-links a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #333333;
      color: #ffffff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <!-- Add Agenda logo image here -->
      <img src="agenda-logo.png" alt="Agenda Logo">
      <h1>Welcome to Agenda!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering with Agenda. Your account has been successfully created, and we're thrilled to have you on board!</p>
      <p>With Agenda, you'll be able to:</p>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">
          <!-- Add task management icon here -->
          <img src="../assets/images/icons/calendar-solid.svg" alt="Task Management">
          <p>Manage Tasks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <!-- Add collaboration icon here -->
          <img src="../assets/images/icons/list-check-solid.svg" alt="Collaboration">
          <p>Collaborate</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <!-- Add analytics icon here -->
          <img src="../assets/images/icons/chart-line-solid.svg" alt="Analytics">
          <p>Track Progress</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>To get started, click the button below to access your dashboard:</p>
      <a href="#" class="cta-button" style="color: white;">Access Your Dashboard</a>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, our support team is always here to help. Don't hesitate to reach out!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The Agenda Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="social-links">
      <!-- Add social media icons here -->
      <a href="#"><img src="../assets/images/icons/facebook-brands-solid.svg" alt="Facebook"></a>
      <a href="#"><img src="../assets/images/icons/twitter-brands-solid.svg" alt="Twitter"></a>
      <a href="#"><img src="../assets/images/icons/linkedin-brands-solid.svg" alt="LinkedIn"></a>
      <a href="#"><img src="../assets/images/icons/instagram-brands-solid.svg" alt="Instagram"></a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Agenda. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>123 Productivity Street, Organization City, TO-DO 12345</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>